response.overview: On September 20, 2017, Osaka Central Gymnasium Sub Arena in Osaka hosted Day 9 of NJPW Road To Destruction 2017.  The main event featured CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Toru Yano & Will Ospreay) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito).  The card also featured War Machine (Hanson & Raymond Rowe) vs Suzuki-gun (Davey Boy Smith Jr., Lance Archer & Takashi Iizuka).  Other wrestlers on the show include Jushin Thunder Liger, Ricochet and Hiroyoshi Tenzan.
response.title: NJPW Road To Destruction 2017: Day 9
